sushy/resources/updateservice/updateserv.message:
I think the point is to construct a full URI of the Task resource (including the scheme and netloc).

The task_uri_data, if present, will be something like: /redfish/v1/TaskService/Tasks/{TaskId}

The task_monitor will be something like: https://example.com/redfish/v1/TaskMonitor/{TaskMonitorId}

If task_uri_data is not None, the resulting task_uri will then be: https://example.com/redfish/v1/TaskService/Tasks/{TaskId}

If task_uri_data is None, the resulting task_uri will be: https://example.com/redfish/v1/TaskMonitor/{TaskMonitorId}
(If there is no task_uri_data, the task_uri will just be the task_monitor.)

Note that if there is no task_monitor, an exception will be raised below on line #166.

